{"tid":506563,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"唉...好唔開心, 今晚去左女朋友屋企做冬","createTime":"2017-12-22T10:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T03:22:56.000Z","uid":116905,"like":11,"dislike":157,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"647d6512b022410e8396d3f6298393f56e2f318d","tid":506563,"uid":116905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:37:47.000Z","msg":"女朋友帶我返佢屋企食冬至飯&hellip;<br />\n一坐低, 我，女友，伯母，伯父<br />\n伯母第一句就問我住邊&hellip;<br />\n(其實呢餐飯係我地第一次見面)<br />\n我就答: 我住公屋 ka&hellip;<br />\n天水圍&hellip;天耀村呀&hellip;不過就租嘅<br />\n早年走寶冇買到&hellip;好後悔呀伯母<br />\n講完呢句都見到伯母面有難色<br />\n咁我都知咩事啦<br />\n呢成餐飯&hellip;係嘅...我會有飯食&hellip;<br />\n可能又有啲肉食下&hellip;<br />\n但係舊雞脾我就唔敢掂<br />\n最後成餐飯伯母都無野再問我&hellip;<br />\n話之我乜大學畢業&hellip;<br />\n幾有上進心幾有目標<br />\n食完飯&hellip;<br />\n伯母終於開聲講野<br />\n佢大聲叫&hellip;<br />\n阿女 送客&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n唉......."},{"pid":"8702e7461a74f12cb606cced8e03b3e32230e885","tid":506563,"uid":36238,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"早左2個鐘出post"},{"pid":"015fc720c046ff3e3278b8bf619aedb8030074b4","tid":506563,"uid":36964,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"潮文有乜好repost<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3320f610d32397ec6b89fad0bf01b62f68364a9e","tid":506563,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"見你咁慘留一留名"},{"pid":"827773980b7d4743aa9aef2a6ecc7cebd99bcaf8","tid":506563,"uid":116905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"真係好唔開心"},{"pid":"137f057abd1902ee43ba4ec2d856d473976c8226","tid":506563,"uid":116905,"like":6,"dislike":67,"score":-61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>潮文有乜好repost<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n威啦老屎忽好型囉得未???"},{"pid":"7bc5d127d58cf517220edc11382204ea98669f0b","tid":506563,"uid":116905,"like